# --- Legacy-audit evidence intake: NEVER commit raw evidence ---
# Exports, inventories, screenshots, and clones can contain
# tokens, cookies, headers, PII, or licensed vendor content.
# Everything under evidence-intake/ stays untracked except its
# README and the .gitkeep markers.
evidence-intake/
!evidence-intake/README.md
legacy-audit/
*.workflow.json
n8n-export*
*-workflows-export*
server-inventory*
billing*.png
billing*.jpg
billing*.pdf
dns-export*
zone-export*
supabase-export*
supabase-backup*
*.dump
*.sql.gz
